      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRUISER MY UNCLE (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Pop Diva (17.26) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and four minor placings from 10 starts. Leading chance again. TULLY'S GEM (2) was in the placings last time but three back posted a slick 17.28 win over 297m at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance. CHAROS JOURNEY (3) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant fifth (18.14) in a Grade 5 over 297m at this track. Better than latest and worth another try. SALUTING CRAIG (7) must be respected at his pet distance.",
